column5: Sweet, gotta love a pikes appetite!
Ya, and about those "too big" 6 inch lures I use.

Very cool, pike and lakers definitely love a burbot snack.  I once caught a big burbot full of pike fry, too lol.  They're not 'freshwater eel' like the guy says though.  There's tons of species of freshwater eel, and burbot ain't one of them.
